---
title: Savoury Chive and Ricotta Pancakes Serves 4 | with Bacon
description: An elegant twist on an old favourite, these fluffy chive and ricotta pancakes are the perfect addition to your brunch table! Drizzle them with maple syrup and serve with salty bacon for the best of sweet and savoury!

Ingredients: 2% Milk (partly skimmed milk, vitamin A palmitate, vitamin D3) (milk) • Bacon (pork, water, salt, sugar, sodium phosphates, sodium erythorbate, sodium nitrite, spices, smoke) • All-purpose flour (wheat) • Ricotta cheese (pasteurized whey, pasteurized milk, citric acid, salt) (milk) • Lemon • Grade A egg • Maple syrup • Baking powder • Chives.
